## ğŸ’» Method 2: Command Line Configs (Flexible)

**Location**: [`99_Outputs/repomix-configs/`](99_Outputs/repomix-configs/)

### Available Profiles:

```powershell
# From anywhere in vault:
.\99_Outputs\repomix-configs\repomix-helper.ps1 notes      # Personal notes only
.\99_Outputs\repomix-configs\repomix-helper.ps1 library    # Reference materials
.\99_Outputs\repomix-configs\repomix-helper.ps1 codebase   # Code from 999-codebas+pkb/
.\99_Outputs\repomix-configs\repomix-helper.ps1 project    # Specific project
.\99_Outputs\repomix-configs\repomix-helper.ps1 custom "path/to/folder"
```

### Direct repomix commands:
```bash
# Use specific config
repomix --config 99_Outputs/repomix-configs/repomix.config.notes-only.json

# Custom run
repomix --output 99_Outputs/my-output.txt --style markdown "02-projects/my-project"
```

