## ğŸ¯ When to Use Which Method

### Use VSCode Extension when:
- âœ… Quick ad-hoc exports
- âœ… Right-click convenience
- âœ… Visual file selection
- âœ… Integrated with IDE workflow

### Use Command Line configs when:
- âœ… Specific profiles (notes/library/codebase)
- âœ… Automated/scripted exports
- âœ… Precise control over output
- âœ… Combining multiple exports

