## ğŸ”’ Safety Features

All repomix outputs are automatically:
- âœ… Ignored by Obsidian (won't cause crashes)
- âœ… Excluded from git commits
- âœ… Located in `99_Outputs/` for easy management
- âœ… Using ignore patterns to skip large folders

