2. Created instruction file for VSCode extension
3. Set up ignore patterns to prevent future crashes
4. Created multiple config profiles for different use cases
5. Documented everything for future reference

### The Result:
- âœ… Obsidian won't crash anymore
- âœ… VSCode extension works properly
- âœ… Flexible command-line options available
